data.description: Low maintenance living with no rear neighbors in one of Meridian's most desirable neighborhoods! The established community of Movado features a community pool, playgrounds, dog park and scenic landscaping & paths, including a creek-side trail. Forget about mowing - the community handles all front & back landscaping and irrigation maintenance! This one-owner home is the Mesa floorplan by Blackrock Homes. The main level offers an open floor plan seamlessly connecting the living room to the spacious dining area and kitchen, complete with quartz counters, a breakfast bar island, gas range, and a convenient half bath. Upstairs, you'll find a large primary bedroom with a full ensuite bath, along with 3 additional bedrooms, a 2nd full bath w/double vanity, and a versatile hallway perfect for a potential office nook.  Excellent location w/easy access to The Village, schools, healthcare, I-84 and only 15 minutes to downtown Boise! Water Softener, garage shelving & RO system installed.
